car_model: 2018 Audi Q5 2.0 TFSI S Tronic quattro
reviewer_info: Posted by Haider Mustafa on Apr 20, 2019
review_text: This is a good, spacious car and has good space at back. The infotainment system is good. Seats are pretty comfortable and heated seats are so nice in winter which come as standard . Has 7 different driving modes from which Dynamic is the best as I use it on motorways quite a lot and get about 30mpg.
